name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
Guangxi University uncovered a student protest tonight.
The reason was that Guangxi University had already had dozens of positive cases, but had not released them, and even held normal exams.
At around 5 pm this afternoon, someone on the Guangxi University Weibo super topic proposed to go to the West Sports Center together at 7 pm.
Then a counselor entered the chat group, causing the group to disband, and the Guangxi University super topic was banned from speaking.
Someone posted that all gathering places on campus were surrounded by security.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Some netizens posted that although there was no gathering of students, a large number of police cars had gathered outside the school gate.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: It is reported that the final solution was to change the name of the quarantine area.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
Tonight, Nanchang University Jiangxi Medical College
Master students gathered to protest, demanding equal pay for equal work.
It is reported that, like the major medical schools before, the students' meager training income of 1,000 yuan per month and heavy clinical affairs overwhelmed them.
About an hour ago, the school gate was locked, there was a police car at the gate, and protests were still going on inside the school.
